   <head>In Neglect</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quintain">
     <l n="1" met="-+-+--+-+">They leave us so to the way we took,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+-+--+-+(-)"> As two in whom they were provedmistaken,</l>
     <l n="3" met="--+-+--+-+">That we sit sometimes in the wayside nook,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+--+--+-+">With mis chievous, vagrant, seraphic look, </l>
     <l n="5" met="-+--+-+-+(-)"> And try if we cannot feel forsaken.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
